name: Safelist_removeEnforcedAttributeTest
description: Unit tests for the removal of enforced attributes in the Safelist class.

test_cases.name: testRemoveEnforcedAttribute_ExistingAttribute
test_cases.description: Tests the removal of an existing enforced attribute from the Safelist.

test_cases.name: testRemoveEnforcedAttribute_NonExistingAttribute
test_cases.description: Tests the removal of a non-existing enforced attribute from the Safelist.

test_cases.name: testRemoveEnforcedAttribute_NonExistingTag
test_cases.description: Tests the removal of an enforced attribute from a non-existing tag in the Safelist.

test_cases.name: testRemoveEnforcedAttribute_EmptyTagAndAttribute
test_cases.description: Tests the removal of an enforced attribute with empty tag and attribute names, expecting an IllegalArgumentException.

test_cases.name: testRemoveEnforcedAttribute_NullTagAndAttribute
test_cases.description: Tests the removal of an enforced attribute with null tag and attribute names, expecting an IllegalArgumentException.
